{
  "schema": 1,
  "id": 70,
  "title": "Update Espanso package to latest (WSL + Windows)",
  "style": "Espanso-Edit",
  "role": "assistant",
  "template": [
    "## Goal",
    "Update the installed Espanso package to the latest version from the Git repo, idempotently.",
    "",
    "## Context",
    "- Repo: https://github.com/josiahH-cf/prompt-automation",
    "- Package name: your-pa",
    "- Branch: v2-scoping-project",
    "- Runbook script: scripts/espanso-package-runbook.sh",
    "",
    "## Output",
    "Provide two fenced blocks users can copy/paste:",
    "1) WSL bash block to run the runbook and verify Windows install",
    "2) Windows PowerShell block (alternative) to update/restart only.",
    "",
    "## WSL Bash Block",
    "```bash",
    "set -euo pipefail",
    "cd /home/josiah/github-cf/prompt-automation",
    "bash scripts/espanso-package-runbook.sh",
    "# verify installed packages on Windows",
    "powershell.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"espanso package list\"",
    "powershell.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"espanso restart\"",
    "```",
    "",
    "## Windows PowerShell Block (alternative)",
    "```powershell",
    "$ErrorActionPreference = 'Stop'",
    "espanso package update your-pa",
    "espanso restart",
    "espanso package list | Select-String -Pattern 'your-pa' -SimpleMatch",
    "```",
    "",
    "## Notes",
    "- If you changed snippets, ensure version was bumped in packages/your-pa/<version>/_manifest.yml or set BUMP_VERSION=true before running the runbook.",
    "- Keep %APPDATA%\\espanso\\match\\base.yml removed/disabled to avoid duplicates with the package.",
    ""
  ],
  "placeholders": [],
  "global_placeholders": {},
